metadata.name: WIH NFT USB-3A
metadata.description: The WIH NFT is a limited digital asset of comprehensive brain health check up and report service using modern medical equipments including 7T MRI and advanced scientific medical tests in the Brain Wellness Center of WIH. Once you own this NFT, you can take brain health screening in the Brain Wellness Center that uses a proprietary method developed in partnership with Harvard Medical School and Massachusetts General Hospital with exclusive member benefits of WIH Bio & Healthcare Platform.
